quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  74,32,“Sichoncho; ndikulumbilira mwezi
  74,33,“Ndi usiku pamene ukuchoka
  74,34,“Ndi m’bandakucha pamene kukuyera
  74,35,"“Ndithu uwo, (moto wa Jahannam) ndi chimodzi mwa malodza akulu"
  74,36,“Ndi chenjezo kwa anthu
  74,37,“Kwa yemwe wafuna mwa inu kutsogola (pochita zabwino zokamthandiza tsiku louka kwa akufa) kapena kutsalira (ndi za m’dziko)
  74,38,“Mzimu uliwonse ukakhala chikole ndi zimene udachita
  74,39,“Kupatula akudzanja lamanja (Asilamu amene adadzimasula okha potembenukira kwa Allah)
  74,40,“(Iwo) adzakhala m’minda (yosasimbika kukongola kwake) akufunsana wina ndi mnzake
  74,41,“Za anthu oipa
  74,42,"“(Kuti): “Nchiyani chakulowetsani ku Moto?”"
  74,43,"“Adzanena: “Sitidali m’gulu la omwe adali kupemphera (Swala)"
  74,44,“Ndiponso sitidali kuwadyetsa masikini
  74,45,“Koma tinkangomira (m’zachabe ndi zabodza) pamodzi ndi omira (m’menemo)
  74,46,“Ndiponso tidali kutsutsa za tsiku la malipiro
  74,47,“Mpaka imfa idatifika.”
  74,48,“Choncho siwudzawathandiza uwomboli wa awomboli
  74,49,“Kodi ali ndi chiyani iwo pakuti azinyozera chenjezoli (limene lili Qur’an)
  74,50,“(Akuyenda mothamanga kuti asamve chenjezoli) ngati kuti iwo ndi mbidzi zothawa
  74,51,“(Zimene) zikuthawa mkango
  74,52,"“Ati akufuna aliyense mwa iwo apatsidwe kalata zotambasulidwa (zimene zitsimikize uthenga wa Mneneri Muhammad{s.a.w)"
  74,53,“Sichoncho! Koma kuti iwo sakuopa tsiku lachimaliziro
  74,54,“Sichoncho! Ndithu ichi (Qur’an) ndichikumbutso (chokwanira)
  74,55,“Choncho amene wafuna achikumbukire (amene sakufuna ndizake)
  74,56,"“Ndipo sangakumbukire pokhapokha Allah atafuna. Iye ndiye Amene ali woyenera kumuopa, ndiponso ndiye Mwini kukhululukira (amene akumuopa)"